Maintenance - The maintenance requirement is calculated based on metabolic body weight (body weight^{0.75}).
Lactating and Dry Cows
CBW = MW * 0.06275 \tag{2.1}
CW = {(18 + (DOP - 190) * 0.665) * ( \frac{CBW}{45}),~\text{if}~DOP &gt; 190.0} \tag{2.2}
Otherwise
NEmaint = 0.08 \times (BW - CW)^{0.75} \tag{2.3}
